const n=JSON.parse('{"key":"v-0d7d3667","path":"/zh/guide/markdown/advanced/echarts.html","title":"ECharts","lang":"zh-CN","frontmatter":{"title":"ECharts","icon":"rank","categories":["Markdown"],"tags":["ECharts","Markdown"],"head":[["meta",{"name":"og:url","content":"/zh/guide/markdown/advanced/echarts.html"}],["meta",{"name":"og:site_name","content":"vuepress-theme-star"}],["meta",{"name":"og:title","content":"ECharts"}],["meta",{"name":"og:description","content":""}],["meta",{"name":"og:type","content":"article"}],["meta",{"name":"og:image","content":""}],["meta",{"name":"og:updated_time","content":"2022-10-08T12:35:43.000Z"}],["meta",{"name":"og:locale","content":"zh-CN"}],["meta",{"name":"og:locale:alternate","content":"en-US"}],["meta",{"name":"og:locale:alternate","content":"zh-CN"}],["meta",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["meta",{"name":"twitter:image:alt","content":"vuepress-theme-star"}],["meta",{"name":"article:author","content":""}],["meta",{"name":"article:tag","content":"ECharts"}],["meta",{"name":"article:tag","content":"Markdown"}],["meta",{"name":"article:published_time","content":""}],["meta",{"name":"article:modified_time","content":"2022-10-08T12:35:43.000Z"}]]},"excerpt":"<h1 id=\\"echarts\\" tabindex=\\"-1\\"><a class=\\"header-anchor\\" href=\\"#echarts\\" aria-hidden=\\"true\\">#</a> ECharts</h1>\\n<p>让你 VuePress 站点中的 Markdown 文件支持 ECharts 图表。</p>\\n<p>使用 <a href=\\"https://echarts.apache.org/zh/index.html\\" target=\\"_blank\\" rel=\\"noopener noreferrer\\">ECharts<ExternalLinkIcon/></a> 提供相应功能。</p>\\n","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"文档","slug":"文档","link":"#文档","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"语法","slug":"语法","link":"#语法","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"案例","slug":"案例","link":"#案例","children":[{"level":3,"title":"折线图","slug":"折线图","link":"#折线图","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"柱状图","slug":"柱状图","link":"#柱状图","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"饼图","slug":"饼图","link":"#饼图","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"散点图","slug":"散点图","link":"#散点图","children":[]}]}],"git":{"createdTime":1664201387000,"updatedTime":1665232543000,"contributors":[{"name":"shentuzhigang","email":"shentuzhigang01@weidian.com","commits":4}]},"copyright":"Copyright © 2021-present Starzkg","filePathRelative":"zh/guide/markdown/advanced/echarts.md","content":"---\\ntitle: ECharts\\nicon: rank\\ncategories:\\n  - Markdown\\ntags:\\n  - ECharts\\n  - Markdown\\n---\\n# ECharts\\n让你 VuePress 站点中的 Markdown 文件支持 ECharts 图表。\\n\\n使用 [ECharts](https://echarts.apache.org/zh/index.html) 提供相应功能。\\n\\n<!-- more -->\\n\\n## 文档\\n\\n相关详情，详见 [ECharts 文档](https://echarts.apache.org/handbook/zh/get-started/).\\n\\n## 语法\\n\\n````md\\n```echarts:json 标题\\n{\\n  // 此处为 ECharts 图表配置\\n}\\n```\\n````\\n\\n我们也支持 `js` 和 `javascript` 的代码块，你应当将导出对象赋值给 `module.exports`。\\n\\n## 案例\\n\\n### 折线图\\n\\n```echarts:json 一个折线图案例\\n{\\n  \\"xAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"category\\",\\n    \\"data\\": [\\"Mon\\", \\"Tue\\", \\"Wed\\", \\"Thu\\", \\"Fri\\", \\"Sat\\", \\"Sun\\"]\\n  },\\n  \\"yAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"value\\"\\n  },\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"data\\": [150, 230, 224, 218, 135, 147, 260],\\n      \\"type\\": \\"line\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n:::: details 代码\\n\\n````md\\n```echarts:json 一个折线图案例\\n{\\n  \\"xAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"category\\",\\n    \\"data\\": [\\"Mon\\", \\"Tue\\", \\"Wed\\", \\"Thu\\", \\"Fri\\", \\"Sat\\", \\"Sun\\"]\\n  },\\n  \\"yAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"value\\"\\n  },\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"data\\": [150, 230, 224, 218, 135, 147, 260],\\n      \\"type\\": \\"line\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n````\\n\\n::::\\n\\n### 柱状图\\n\\n```echarts:json 一个柱状图案例\\n{\\n  \\"xAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"category\\",\\n    \\"data\\": [\\"Mon\\", \\"Tue\\", \\"Wed\\", \\"Thu\\", \\"Fri\\", \\"Sat\\", \\"Sun\\"]\\n  },\\n  \\"yAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"value\\"\\n  },\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"data\\": [120, 200, 150, 80, 70, 110, 130],\\n      \\"type\\": \\"bar\\",\\n      \\"showBackground\\": true,\\n      \\"backgroundStyle\\": {\\n        \\"color\\": \\"rgba(180, 180, 180, 0.2)\\"\\n      }\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n:::: details 代码\\n\\n````md\\n```echarts:json 一个柱状图案例\\n{\\n  \\"xAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"category\\",\\n    \\"data\\": [\\"Mon\\", \\"Tue\\", \\"Wed\\", \\"Thu\\", \\"Fri\\", \\"Sat\\", \\"Sun\\"]\\n  },\\n  \\"yAxis\\": {\\n    \\"type\\": \\"value\\"\\n  },\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"data\\": [120, 200, 150, 80, 70, 110, 130],\\n      \\"type\\": \\"bar\\",\\n      \\"showBackground\\": true,\\n      \\"backgroundStyle\\": {\\n        \\"color\\": \\"rgba(180, 180, 180, 0.2)\\"\\n      }\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n````\\n\\n::::\\n\\n### 饼图\\n\\n```echarts:json 一个基础南丁格尔玫瑰图案例\\n{\\n  \\"legend\\": {\\n    \\"top\\": \\"bottom\\"\\n  },\\n  \\"toolbox\\": {\\n    \\"show\\": true,\\n    \\"feature\\": {\\n      \\"mark\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true\\n      },\\n      \\"dataView\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true,\\n        \\"readOnly\\": false\\n      },\\n      \\"restore\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true\\n      },\\n      \\"saveAsImage\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true\\n      }\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"name\\": \\"Nightingale Chart\\",\\n      \\"type\\": \\"pie\\",\\n      \\"radius\\": [20, 100],\\n      \\"center\\": [\\"50%\\", \\"50%\\"],\\n      \\"roseType\\": \\"area\\",\\n      \\"itemStyle\\": {\\n        \\"borderRadius\\": 8\\n      },\\n      \\"data\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 40,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 1\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 38,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 2\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 32,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 3\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 30,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 4\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 28,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 5\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 26,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 6\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 22,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 7\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 18,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 8\\"\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n:::: details 代码\\n\\n````md\\n```echarts:json 一个基础南丁格尔玫瑰图案例\\n{\\n  \\"legend\\": {\\n    \\"top\\": \\"bottom\\"\\n  },\\n  \\"toolbox\\": {\\n    \\"show\\": true,\\n    \\"feature\\": {\\n      \\"mark\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true\\n      },\\n      \\"dataView\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true,\\n        \\"readOnly\\": false\\n      },\\n      \\"restore\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true\\n      },\\n      \\"saveAsImage\\": {\\n        \\"show\\": true\\n      }\\n    }\\n  },\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"name\\": \\"Nightingale Chart\\",\\n      \\"type\\": \\"pie\\",\\n      \\"radius\\": [20, 100],\\n      \\"center\\": [\\"50%\\", \\"50%\\"],\\n      \\"roseType\\": \\"area\\",\\n      \\"itemStyle\\": {\\n        \\"borderRadius\\": 8\\n      },\\n      \\"data\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 40,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 1\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 38,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 2\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 32,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 3\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 30,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 4\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 28,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 5\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 26,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 6\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 22,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 7\\"\\n        },\\n        {\\n          \\"value\\": 18,\\n          \\"name\\": \\"rose 8\\"\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n````\\n\\n::::\\n\\n### 散点图\\n\\n```echarts:json 一个散点图案例\\n{\\n  \\"xAxis\\": {},\\n  \\"yAxis\\": {},\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"symbolSize\\": 20,\\n      \\"data\\": [\\n        [10.0, 8.04],\\n        [8.07, 6.95],\\n        [13.0, 7.58],\\n        [9.05, 8.81],\\n        [11.0, 8.33],\\n        [14.0, 7.66],\\n        [13.4, 6.81],\\n        [10.0, 6.33],\\n        [14.0, 8.96],\\n        [12.5, 6.82],\\n        [9.15, 7.2],\\n        [11.5, 7.2],\\n        [3.03, 4.23],\\n        [12.2, 7.83],\\n        [2.02, 4.47],\\n        [1.05, 3.33],\\n        [4.05, 4.96],\\n        [6.03, 7.24],\\n        [12.0, 6.26],\\n        [12.0, 8.84],\\n        [7.08, 5.82],\\n        [5.02, 5.68]\\n      ],\\n      \\"type\\": \\"scatter\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n\\n:::: details 代码\\n\\n````md\\n```echarts:json 一个散点图案例\\n{\\n  \\"xAxis\\": {},\\n  \\"yAxis\\": {},\\n  \\"series\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\"symbolSize\\": 20,\\n      \\"data\\": [\\n        [10.0, 8.04],\\n        [8.07, 6.95],\\n        [13.0, 7.58],\\n        [9.05, 8.81],\\n        [11.0, 8.33],\\n        [14.0, 7.66],\\n        [13.4, 6.81],\\n        [10.0, 6.33],\\n        [14.0, 8.96],\\n        [12.5, 6.82],\\n        [9.15, 7.2],\\n        [11.5, 7.2],\\n        [3.03, 4.23],\\n        [12.2, 7.83],\\n        [2.02, 4.47],\\n        [1.05, 3.33],\\n        [4.05, 4.96],\\n        [6.03, 7.24],\\n        [12.0, 6.26],\\n        [12.0, 8.84],\\n        [7.08, 5.82],\\n        [5.02, 5.68]\\n      ],\\n      \\"type\\": \\"scatter\\"\\n    }\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\\n````\\n\\n::::\\n\\n","icon":"rank","author":[{"name":"shentuzhigang","email":"shentuzhigang01@weidian.com"}],"top":false,"length":717,"words":717,"readingTime":2.39}');export{n as data};
